{"tid":1985791,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【罕有片段】汪 明 荃 專 訪 李 嘉 欣 大 美 人 無 懼 飾 演 粗 口 角 色","createTime":"2020-04-23T11:39:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-25T04:49:11.000Z","uid":24160,"like":22,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"f460840d248227fcbfe31da3a5e9fbad91e23745","tid":1985791,"uid":24160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T11:39:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://streamable.com/dthrbi\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstreamable.com%2Fdthrbi&d=7FLALsszV4LuAMmN05fc6qix4Ji0%2BaXPUR6dcaOs6Zo%3D&h=e2e73862\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://streamable.com/dthrbi</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wZhoNHi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwZhoNHi.png&h=53bba180&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n汪明荃翹腳展露誘人美腿先問及李嘉欣工作背景<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ek11znh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEk11znh.png&h=14af5a79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n剛選完港姐，李嘉欣表示收到第一份劇本便很熱愛演戲了<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/D8qRcbw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FD8qRcbw.png&h=5ca1ddc8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n並表示粗口角可以演活另一面的性格<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EmqasHh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEmqasHh.png&h=f1693f93&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n身穿低胸長裙坦露白滑肌膚的汪明荃問及李嘉欣何以半年前控告記者？<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Bdls9m0.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FBdls9m0.gif&h=6bd76453&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n李嘉欣邊聽邊點頭微笑<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/q0SL1ca.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fq0SL1ca.png&h=3113f44c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n長氣的阿姐又道出一般明星應對記者的做法，會互相配合的<br />\n汪明荃再問點解有呢個舉動呢？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WwfhSjV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWwfhSjV.png&h=883dd5e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FgsDBLw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFgsDBLw.png&h=d3e15ae9&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n李嘉欣繼續耐心聆聽<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oLcj5F3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoLcj5F3.png&h=10fab862&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n李嘉欣表示傳媒要尊重藝人立場，必先經過藝人訪問才報導<br />\n<br />\n汪明荃實際面對傳媒做法<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/s60wfBS.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fs60wfBS.gif&h=ff60bfe9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"65d89242b13ad92d0ae16d62ece2ef3300e4b373","tid":1985791,"uid":24160,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T11:39:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/cAg0Day.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FcAg0Day.gif&h=7884fa01&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0d2ce787206ca9a074d1dd78ca7b6e78e1eab7a6","tid":1985791,"uid":3189,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T11:41:34.000Z","msg":"戀戀芭比 同 李嘉欣 呢兩位大美人fans會唔會入嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7aa0a6bdd07e8309b24d283afb3a0fb81418a4ed","tid":1985791,"uid":24160,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"0d2ce787206ca9a074d1dd78ca7b6e78e1eab7a6","tid":1985791,"uid":3189,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T11:41:34.000Z","msg":"戀戀芭比 同 李嘉欣 呢兩位大美人fans會唔會入嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T11:43:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://photouploads.com/images/3d797d.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotouploads.com%2Fimages%2F3d797d.gif&h=eda1a8a6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"07ba4ea0367845ca12c2c10ceff707cc119de52e","tid":1985791,"uid":185631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T11:43:26.000Z","msg":"食花生"},{"pid":"326b86467f6b9b6200654687de05dcc1413f5b49","tid":1985791,"uid":27520